name: VANCOUVER PLANE SPOTTING! Heavy Traffic at YVR [4K]
description:
Back in the fall, I paid a visit to Vancouver International Airport - the second busiest airport in Canada by passenger traffic!

It's a major hub for Air Canada as well as WestJet, and has an exceptionally diverse lineup of international carriers from Europe, Asia, and Oceania.

Enjoy this full day's worth of YVR plane spotting in some exceptionally clear weather!
